Subject: RFQ — 5000 shipper cartons for Q3 launch

Hi team,

Following our phone call, please quote for the following for our July launch:

- Quantity: 5,000 boxes
- Style: RSC (FEFCO 0201)
- Internal dimensions: 400 x 300 x 250 mm
- Board: 3-ply, B-flute
  - Outer: Kraft liner 200 GSM
  - Medium: Semi-chem fluting 120 GSM
  - Inner: Test liner 170 GSM
- Print: 2-color flexo, coverage around 40%
- Finishing: die-cutting
- Glued joint
- Required at our Pune DC by 30 June 2026

We'll raise a PO as soon as the quote lands. Please confirm earliest despatch.

Thanks,
Rajesh Menon
Purchase — Acme Brands Pvt Ltd
ops@acmebrands.in | +91 98765 43210`},{label:"Novus — Mailer, 4C offset",summary:"New prospect, D2C mailer with premium finishing.",body:`Hi,

We're a subscription-box startup (Novus Home) launching in August and
need 10,000 tuck-top mailers for our unboxing experience. Specs below:

 • Box style: crash-lock mailer, tuck top
 • Dimensions: 280 x 200 x 80 mm (OD)
 • Board: 350 GSM SBS, single wall — premium feel
 • Print: 4-color offset, full bleed (around 95% coverage)
 • Finishing: matte lamination + spot varnish on logo
 • Joint: glued

Target delivery: last week of August 2026, to our Bengaluru warehouse.
Quantities may scale to 25k/month if the pilot lands, so pricing at
break quantities of 10k / 25k / 50k would be great.

Who's the right person to loop in on artwork hand-off?

Thanks!
— Priya, Novus Home
priya@novushome.co`},{label:"Taj Foods — rush, partial spec",summary:"Existing customer, urgent turnaround, some spec missing.",body:`Subject: URGENT — need 2000 boxes in 10 days
From: arjun@tajfoods.com

Team,

We have an export order that we need to despatch by 3 May 2026 and are
short on cartons. Need 2,000 shippers (same construction as the last
batch you supplied — the brown 5-ply we use for the 15-kg basmati).
Internal dims 500 x 350 x 300 mm. No print required, plain brown.

Please confirm by EOD whether you can turn this around — happy to pay
rush charges.

Arjun | Taj Foods Exports`},{label:"Globex — vague, needs follow-up",summary:"Spec-light enquiry; agent should flag low confidence.",body:`Hello,

Could you send me a price for about 1000 small cardboard boxes? They're
for shipping spare parts. Nothing fancy, just brown. Let me know what
you can do.

Regards,
M. Kowalski
Globex Components`},{label:"Patel Pharma — folding carton",summary:"Pharma carton, tamper-evident, regulated print.",body:`From: procurement@patelpharma.in
Subject: Quotation request — paracetamol folding carton, 100k

Dear Sir/Madam,

Please quote for the following secondary packaging carton:

Item:        Folding carton, reverse tuck-end (RTE)
Qty:         100,000 units
Dimensions:  85 x 40 x 150 mm (L x W x H)
Material:    Duplex board 300 GSM, white back
Print:       2-color offset (Pantone 293 + black), coverage ~70%
Finishing:   UV varnish on print side, die-cut, embossed logo panel
Joint:       glued, tamper-evident seal
Compliance:  must meet our pharma pack QA spec (copy attached separately)

Delivery:    in tranches of 25k — first tranche by 15 June 2026, balance over
             the following 8 weeks to our Ahmedabad plant.

Kindly share your best rate along with lead time and MOQ.

Thanks,
Deepa Iyer
Procurement, Patel Pharma Ltd`}];function uA(t){return t>=.75?"bg-emerald-50 text-emerald-700 border-emerald-200":t>=.5?"bg-amber-50 text-amber-800 border-amber-200":"bg-rose-50 text-rose-700 border-rose-200"}function mA(t){return t==="approved"?"bg-emerald-50 text-emerald-700 border-emerald-200":t==="rejected"?"bg-slate-100 text-slate-600 border-slate-200":"bg-sky-50 text-sky-700 border-sky-200"}function xA(t){const n=new Date(t).getTime();if(Number.isNaN(n))return t;const s=Date.now()-n,a=Math.round(s/6e4);if(a<1)return"just now";if(a<60)return`${a}m ago`;const r=Math.round(a/60);if(r<24)return`${r}h ago`;const i=Math.round(r/24);return i<7?`${i}d ago`:new Date(t).toLocaleDateString()}function hA({onJobCreated:t}){const n=zn(),s=Hs(),[a,r]=u.useState([]),[i,l]=u.useState([]),[o,d]=u.useState([]),[c,m]=u.useState("pending"),[h,x]=u.useState(""),[p,g]=u.useState(!1),[y,j]=u.useState(null),f=u.useRef(null),b=u.useRef(null),[v,_]=u.useState(null),[k,w]=u.useState([]),[N,E]=u.useState(null),[R,F]=u.useState(1e4),[M,T]=u.useState(null),[$,C]=u.useState(!1),[P,S]=u.useState(null),[Q,O]=u.useState(null),[K,L]=u.useState({}),[z,J]=u.useState(null),[Y,U]=u.useState(!1),[G,V]=u.useState(null),[H,B]=u.useState(null),[q,Z]=u.useState({name:"",email:"",contact_person:"",phone:"",location:""}),[ae,ue]=u.useState(""),[he,xe]=u.useState(!1),[fe,ye]=u.useState(!1),[ce,_e]=u.useState(null),[Ne,Me]=u.useState(null),[qe,dt]=u.useState(null),[nt,jt]=u.useState(null),[ze,Ct]=u.useState({}),[Re,Ke]=u.useState(!1),we=()=>{FL().then(D=>r(D.data)).catch(()=>{})};u.useEffect(()=>{we(),Fb().then(D=>l(D.data)).catch(()=>{}),is().then(D=>d(D.data)).catch(()=>{}),em({is_active:!0}).then(D=>w(D.data)).catch(()=>{})},[]);const De=u.useMemo(()=>{if(!v||!k.length)return[];if(v.carton_or_leaflet==="leaflet")return[];const D=Number(v.gsm)||0,ge=String(v.material||"").toLowerCase(),ve=new Set(["from","and","or","the","a","an","of","with","for"]),I=ge.replace(/[(),./\\]/g," ").split(/\s+/).filter(se=>se